Hi71nX0.jpg)\n##### 發售日期：未公布\n##### 圖片來源：[**XM Studios**](https://www.xm-studios.com/pages/default.aspx)','https://i.imgur.com/yUZo9tD.png','','新聞','2021-02-10 19:48:26',0,0,0,1,0,0,'',12,7),(376,'Premium Collectibles Studio(PCS)《快打旋風》1/4比例全身雕像「布蘭卡」兩種版本同步販售！','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### Premium Collectibles Studio(PCS)雕像品牌的《快打旋風》系列近日發布了在[**Sideshow Collectibles**](https://www.sideshow.com/)的**1/4比例全身雕像「布蘭卡」** 官方圖片與訊息，會在當地時間2月11日開放預購，尚未公布發售日期。\n\n##### 布蘭卡曾經是正常的人類，飛機的失事導致他變成了綠皮膚與擁有發電的能力，初次登場是在《快打旋風2》，慢慢轉變成綠色皮膚和紅色頭髮的樣子。\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/7Q4GjUp.jpg)\n\n\n##### 布蘭卡全身綠色的皮膚伴隨著大量的肌肉線條，最明顯的對比就是那一頭豪放的紅色毛髮跟褲子，手指與腳趾都是尖銳的白色指甲，他站在長滿藤蔓與青苔的樹枝上，樹木已經長穿了底下的小木屋。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/zFydzpw.jpg)\n\n##### PCS還有推出藍色毛髮與黃色皮膚的Player 2版本，售價都是600美元，將會同步開放預購。\n\n![1](https://i.imgur.com/svrtBsW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/UPk0XGt.jpg)\n\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Hvcbz7X.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/RjsP3d9.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/zQWEBqK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/YiZ6bOW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DcndaIK.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/b7jBLgv.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6MNhFNp.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hEkWTJg.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/zMNklZF.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/KZiow0O.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xbZ6uCG.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高26.67吋｜寬16.46吋｜長13.55吋\n##### 預購價格：兩款皆600美元 約16,795新台幣\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Y1vBPmZ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/FUhkTDx.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/jemIhNf.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/WKkidCL.jpg)\n##### 發售日期：未公布\n##### 圖片來源：[**Sideshow Collectibles**](https://www.sideshow.com/)','https://i.imgur.com/Ji4yJfy.jpg','https://i.imgur.com/p4nrihz.jpg','新聞','2021-02-10 19:49:07',1,0,0,1,0,0,'',19,7),(377,'Prime 1 Studio《神力女超人漫畫》1/3比例全身雕像「神力女超人重生版」','想準時知道最新的玩具新聞，記得按讚追蹤[**一直頑粉絲專頁**](https://www.facebook.com/%E4%B8%80%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%91-107594257704279)\n\n##### 日本雕像品牌**Prime 1 Studio**旗下WonderWoman (comics)系列在[**官網**](https://www.prime1studio.com/)發布了開放預購的 **《神力女超人漫畫》1/3比例全身雕像「神力女超人」** 官方圖片與訊息，將於2022年5-8月發售。\n\n##### 戴安娜是宙斯與亞馬遜女王希波的私生女，擁有半神族的血統，且是希臘最偉大的戰士。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/TiqoofK.jpg)\n\n##### 戴安娜身穿紅色胸甲和藍色皮革的角鬥士裙子，披風可調整和可拆卸，左手拿著雅典娜之劍，右手則是拿著亞馬遜盾牌，盾牌上有著滿滿的雕刻細節，並在腰間配戴真言套索，戴安娜單腳站在雲朵狀的岩石上，下面還有《神力女超人》的標誌性圖案。\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xG0hcDG.jpg)\n\n##### 尺寸：高74.7公分｜寬48.5公分｜長47.1公分\n##### 預購價格：1,099美元 約30,761新台幣\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Ix5PLx2.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/beHedj3.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/dphEkJj.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/z2bnyPr.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/huON3Jl.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xeUt0fk.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/lfrHAd0.jpg)\n\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/v0vz7AJ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/xEtUJxC.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/gwSHVod.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/6zXf8I9.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/dooISmj.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/1nDMpMw.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/NiBZKVi.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/rIBx0WW.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/cPsKByQ.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/ItXDitp.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vuEJWyz.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4a0F0XN.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/4l9cs92.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/hoEt3xF.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/wCRVBN4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/A6Mtlox.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/9mlSDf0.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/z9VF6Hl.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vdPOvy1.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/mhqqOX4.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/vYROrFy.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/DBcJWiz.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/3Uu7oEd.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/fnVo2vi.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/GA5DWbt.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/SLUEomI.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/jNhrrWb.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/Vl2yK6e.jpg)\n\n![](https://i.imgur.com/uRsbmp8.jpg)\n##### 發售日期：2022年5-8月\n##### 圖片來源：[**Prime 1 Studio**](https://www.prime1studio.com/)','https://i.imgur.com/sGtEucO.jpg','','新聞',